{"type": "article", "id": 26864, "title": "模块型家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-16T06:45:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160608130731ThAXdtPBfRqWjJbG.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>想让坐沙发变成像玩游戏一样有趣的体验？<a href=\"http://www.carloratti.com/\">Carlo Ratti Associati</a> 推出的 <a href=\"http://www.lift-bit.com./\">Lift-Bit</a> 可以满足你的这个梦想。它是一套由六边形模块组成的家具系统，每个模块都可以根据需要调整高度。你可以用手势指引它调节，或者使用配套的手机应用。你可以通过<a href=\"http://www.makrshakr.com/wordpress/product/single-lift-bit/\">链接</a>订购这个奇妙的家具，单个模块的价格为 799 欧元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130729hiaBy3ucQbZUPFek.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.41166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130729JmVbjEdeGqlKA0v1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130730JvW1f9gLqQZzurV5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.39333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130730rIbkMxa0w7fOvXs6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.92166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}